Class LoadProfile

java.lang.Object
org.apache.wayang.core.optimizer.costs.LoadProfile

Serializable, JsonSerializable
public class LoadProfile extends Object implements JsonSerializable, Serializable
Reflects the (estimated) required resources of an Operator or FunctionDescriptor.
